%% Trace: features/01-Email註冊.feature → contracts/01-雙管道註冊.yml#signUpByMail
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Captcha as CaptchaProvider
    participant Ctrl as SignUpController
    participant Svc as MemberRegistrationService
    participant CRM as CrmCustomerGateway
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>FE: 輸入 Email + 密碼 + Captcha
    FE->>Captcha: 驗證 Captcha token
    Captcha-->>FE: ok
    FE->>Ctrl: POST /sign-up/mail (email, password, captcha)
    Ctrl->>Svc: register(email, password)
    Svc->>CRM: lookupCustomer(emailHash)
    CRM-->>Svc: NONE (NEW)
    Svc->>CRM: createCustomer(email)
    CRM-->>Svc: customer_id
    Svc->>Repo: insert MemberAuth(customer_id, email, email_hash, password_hash)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT member_auths
    DB-->>Repo: id
    Svc->>Repo: insert MemberCenterProfile(member_auth_id, member_id)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT member_center_profiles
    Svc-->>Ctrl: registered
    Ctrl-->>FE: 201 Created
    FE-->>User: 註冊成功，導向登入
